Package: ucsStyle
Title: UCS ggplot Theme Using Gotham and Brand Palette (Light/Dark)
Version: 0.1.4
Authors@R: person(given = "David", family = "Reichmuth", email = "dreichmuth@ucsusa.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: David Reichmuth <dreichmuth@ucsusa.org>
Description: Provides a UCS-style ggplot2 theme using the Gotham font, plus
    helpers to register Gotham from Windows per-user AppData fonts and brand
    colour palettes with convenient ggplot2 scales. Includes a dark-background
    theme variant and a saver that defaults to 1500x900 px with PNG/JPG/SVG/PDF support.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.5)
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    showtext,
    sysfonts,
    grDevices,
    ragg,
    svglite
Suggests:
    tools
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
